  <h1>Toast Notifications</h1>
  <p class="lead">Toast patterns for non-blocking notifications with variants, positions, and JavaScript API.</p>

  <section>
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <layout-text>
      <p>The toast component uses the <code>&lt;toast-wc&gt;</code> web component to display non-blocking notifications. Toasts require JavaScript to show dynamically but provide a clean API for common use cases like form feedback and status updates.</p>
      <p><strong>Key features:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Four semantic variants: info, success, warning, error</li>
        <li>Six position options (corners and center edges)</li>
        <li>Auto-dismiss with configurable duration</li>
        <li>Manual dismiss option</li>
        <li>Multiple toasts stack automatically</li>
      </ul>
    </layout-text>
  </section>

