  <section>
    <h2>Usage Notes</h2>
    <layout-text>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Single container:</strong> Only place one toast-wc container per page</li>
        <li><strong>Position:</strong> Use <code>top-end</code> for most applications (top-right in LTR)</li>
        <li><strong>Duration:</strong> Use shorter durations (2-3s) for success messages, longer or manual for errors</li>
        <li><strong>Stacking:</strong> Multiple toasts automatically stack vertically</li>
        <li><strong>Accessibility:</strong> Toasts use ARIA live regions for screen reader announcements</li>
      </ul>
    </layout-text>
  </section>

